Ruth Franklin's Artistic Touch https://www.ruthfranklinbonnaz.com/posts/bonnaz/ -<p>Ruth Franklin covers everything from machine operation, troubleshooting machine problems, industry professionalism to pricing embroidery work. Every page contains details regarding bonnaz embroidery and comes with the authority and experience of a 40+ year veteran. It is highly recommended that all chain stitch operators have a printed copy of this book to reference.</p>
<p>Extra effort when digitizing the original documents was taken to also allow for searching the pdf for keywords and phrase matches. For example, this should make the book even more accessible and useful when searching for Cornely looper timing or how to troubleshoot inconsistent stitches. Ctrl+F is your friend.</p>
